<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="furthest-adj-adv">furthest <strong><em>adj &amp; adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'fɜːðɪst/    美 /'fɜːrðɪst/  </p>
<p>[far的最高级]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-farthest">1.★ <strong>(距离、时间上) 最远的 / 地(farthest)；最大程度的 / 地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Which of these cities is the <strong>furthest from</strong> us?
这些城市哪个离我们最远？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Tom can throw the ball furthest.
汤姆能把球掷得最远。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His book has gone furthest in explaining these events.
对于这些事件，他的书解释得最透彻。</p></div></div>